xt-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6ae031e6-500d-4b3a-811a-c4ddced239e0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5cddc945-15da-4e79-879d-15282a7e494c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">높은 동적 범위(HDR) 조명</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8b2f0b31-d131-4ce5-9c65-6dd74852f82d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1a7d82ae-34b1-4282-bd69-616af19c87bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시네마틱 스포트라이트 및</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f6def06d-dc13-44d9-b033-c76e593d3855\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b0816dbc-504b-46cc-94a7-9cb3f9ac135b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로고 뒤에서 발산하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ee942a6f-e650-4517-bf4d-755c7465ed20\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-309783c2-0d6c-4b11-9d3e-76b5f838b424\" style=\"color:#555555;\">볼류메트릭(Volumetric) 발광 효과.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3af25745-24ff-40e3-a075-d20a26bd9218\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f8115a40-4878-4d91-855b-399bb1e35769\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a2ca872d-dd55-485c-a7fb-6f1f804771cd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1f919fbb-6125-4a9c-9779-e956b158a571\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사운드 (Sound)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb757fd1-f63d-4ae9-af71-e2aaca6888e7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-596fe089-1c6e-4197-ba02-836a8f1568b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오직 음향 효과만 사용</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-99308939-7be4-4ee0-8602-ae60c3b83723\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ad8ebb28-6dec-446e-9b3e-e34fb868f434\" style=\"color:#555555;\">강렬한 라이저(Risers),</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e56edf47-100e-47ef-9636-8f004bff7e52\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-76ad61c3-9c2b-463c-aafd-5c0dea38c827\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시네마틱 우우웅 소리(Whooshes),</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5d0edac0-adc6-447f-b582-2bb39c5fcff3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8325bc73-0894-44fa-b796-d2e6166dbfda\" style=\"color:#555555;\">저음의 쿵 소리(Low-end Booms),</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f4556c2d-72b4-43d4-b25d-a859d381eed1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b16c6e4f-5794-4c78-9d7e-1b63847c3be6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로고 충격음</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-94ab2a04-f076-4412-bf28-0751e56f4566\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-25177abf-75ed-448a-9e71-726d21e36db2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-11a2202a-83e7-4583-9185-93c6b0aa21a9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-872dfa84-5a67-476c-8778-2fdb72632a84\" style=\"color:#555555;\">음성 해설이나 내레이션은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-145501f7-5728-4c8e-ba52-405ec5946ba6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d0319916-16a7-4288-a003-695283253084\" style=\"color:#555555;\">포함하지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-187a3842-ae1b-43ac-ae20-d465fada0fa3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-feb5d9a0-9629-4041-b523-ade7b1adaa99\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-02b08be4-69ad-4c51-907f-c90d5bfc5337\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1975a35a-369a-40e0-aa31-efef30fb3dd3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>길이 (Duration)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dad0ab0b-8e86-4e45-8f7f-01e62206f0d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99a0aeb8-9c32-4249-8970-029e425ee189\" style=\"color:#555555;\">약 7.8초</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2576e8d0-f7d2-41b7-ad82-d7e6b164d2c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0e696f75-4f11-48ac-aa78-5073d0db4390\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-006ad389-4b04-4cdc-ad34-6314d2fc985d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d1fadaa5-7607-4da6-b90a-93884b0a6856\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>결과물 (Output)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1cec1926-dcfe-4162-a179-9b7028779935\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-873158f7-3f0b-426e-a060-2540a5d0ea29\" style=\"color:#555555;\">16:9 화면 비율</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7179bca0-fc98-4465-a51f-d609700f1b84\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c0a7f7c5-e94a-44ba-bfd9-b70b591e5fff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">4K 해상도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0193189f-1b99-4acc-97de-e274100a2c00\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2fa90c11-3975-4eb2-8c05-7543a76c4fcd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-43a10352-317a-4f93-9617-9264afcd202d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e2b66481-200a-4fa0-b62a-a39aa400f912\" style=\"color:#555555;\">마지막 프레임</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fee0e51a-b977-4645-91de-82477c91a011\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9d6e9eb1-9290-4f21-8d31-64bffa9b436c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로고가 중앙에 위치하며 빛나고,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a4a5f2e3-2dce-4dfd-979d-ebf1ba054936\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f1ebccc1-cf70-4362-a65a-5f8d38259d47\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주변 소리가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6779b42b-0531-413f-a501-5887b3f1be6c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-04e799e3-c82f-4824-8914-8657a24af5dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">서서히 사라지며(Fade-out),</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-209c2e32-8c61-4c5b-8460-a6d077eca36a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-140b9a7d-c54a-4bfc-bac9-8f9724ef7b9e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">충격음이 울려 퍼지는(Echoing Impact)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1d3eafd1-a3e2-4d73-bff7-22dad2f79f58\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8a903d11-0bc5-4757-84d8-6652625abbeb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">형태로 마무리됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-293e8987-d04c-4071-bd9a-43e999d40f05\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-22903ee5-45df-476b-a9c0-0fae4ac4777c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e61f983b-0925-4e5e-acbb-c33fe91064f9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-720f5a1f-e3ec-4d32-9b8c-3a7c65757a97\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제 AI에 대한 홍보 글과 영상을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-db3c92be-3cc5-4c7a-88e7-d6d507c9a5f8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cda5ebef-dd18-4416-a948-15b64e59095a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">간간이 올려 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-04074606-f82a-4d26-a3f6-8ae0db1a06a8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5d26393f-279f-4f8b-9d08-5bf001d9e06e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-19ee4a32-3749-4300-b13b-39a20a83c9e8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e7be4fba-e128-4965-92c4-8cfb69dca230\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 글을 읽는 고객님의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e18f7e82-59e3-44f6-8086-764917263e26\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0fb9db42-a80f-41da-a6f3-cdef4ee52114\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로고만 주시면 제가 8초짜리 영상을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c039db21-3b8b-4417-a9c2-7cfc0674c1e9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d27ee98f-882e-45e9-a26c-1eb482f50a2f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만드시는 법을 알려드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1ea3fbd3-fa5a-47cb-b43a-7529d6f6f6b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5c52c627-32b0-476d-8b40-c7fbaf31501a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}